cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet from the expected network, will cause unreachable routing and prevent NG interface establishment.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 地址設定為 '10.0.0.1'，該地址位於與預期網路不同的子網中，會導致無法到達的路由，並阻止 NG 介面建立。

du.explanation_en: Changing the absolute SSB frequency from 641280 (band 78) to 1282560 (band 3) creates a frequency misalignment, causing synchronization failures and cell search issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將絕對 SSB 頻率從 641280（頻段 78）更改為 1282560（頻段 3）會造成頻率錯位，導致同步失敗和細胞搜尋問題。
